Toscafund Asset Management LLP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 9:40 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Toscafund Asset Management LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Toscafund Asset Management LLP is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to corporations and businesses. The firm also manages equity mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. Toscafund Asset Management LLP was founded in 2000 and is based in London, United Kingdom.


7th Floor90 Long AcreLondon,  WC2E 9RAUnited KingdomFounded in 2000



Phone: 44 20 7845 6100

Fax: 44 20 7845 6101

www.toscafund.com







