Toscafund Asset Management LLP Key Developments

Healthcare Australia Is Up For Sale
Jul 18 17
Healthcare Australia Pty Ltd. is being prepared for sale. Street Talk can reveal 333 Capital, has been hired to find a buyer for the business, with an auction to get underway early next year. Healthcare Australia is owned by Ares Management, L.P. (NYSE:ARES) and Toscafund Asset Management LLP. Logical acquirers include Randstad Holding NV (ENXTAM:RAND), Adecco Group AG (SWX:ADEN) and Recruit Holdings Co.,Ltd. (TSE:6098).


Toscafund Mulls Options For San Leon
Apr 26 17
Toscafund Asset Management LLP (AIM:SLE) which holds 59.52% of the issued share capital of San Leon Energy Plc (AIM:SLE), has informed the company that it has appointed Hannam & Partners (Advisory) LLP to conduct a review of the strategic options available to Toscafund. It understands that Hannam & Partners has initiated an exercise to educate a small number of parties on the key assets and valuation of San Leon. This exercise had been conducted independently of SLE's board, management and advisers and was initiated more than three months after SLE's approach announcement.


Toscafund Reportedly In Talks To Acquire 15% In easyProperty
Dec 8 15
Toscafund Asset Management LLP plans to acquire an interest of around 15% in easyProperty for about £15 million, Sky News reported citing people in the know. A deal expected to be announced later this week.


