Ares, Toscafund To Buy Rest Of Healthcare Locums Stock



        By Jake Simpson



					Law360, New York (April 11, 2013,  3:33 PM EDT) -- A joint venture by U.K. private equity firm Toscafund Asset Management LLP and Los Angeles-based debt and equity financier Ares Capital Corp. has agreed to acquired all of the outstanding shares of London-based staffing solutions firm Healthcare Locums PLC for 0.75 pence per share in cash, Healthcare Locums said Thursday.The firm agreed to accept the consortium's offer, which is a 47.1 percent premium to Healthcare Locums' closing price of 0.51 pence on the London Stock Exchange on Wednesday. Ares Capital Europe Ltd. and Toscafund already...
				
